      <!-- Deferral Filtering Funnel — transparency on why most works can't be deferred -->
      <ScrollReveal>
        <div class="funnel-section">
          <h3 class="intel-subheading">Why Can't LCC Just Delay These?</h3>
          <p class="intel-desc">
            Of {totalWorks} roadworks in Burnley, {lccWorksCount} are LCC's own works and {utilityWorksCount} are utilities
            (BT, Cadent, ENWL, UU, IX Wireless, Virgin Media). LCC can defer its own planned works,
