          <p class="section-subtitle">Different organisations are responsible for different parts of the road network</p>
        </div>
        <div class="resp-grid stagger-children">
          <div class="resp-card">
            <span class="resp-badge" style="background: rgba(18, 182, 207, 0.12); color: #12b6cf;">County Council</span>
            <h3>Lancashire County Council</h3>
